{"word":"H6586 - פָּשַׁע - pâshaʻ - paw-shah' - Offend","slug":"H6586","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">פָּשַׁע</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>pâshaʻ"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>paw-shah'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Offend"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E4;&#x05BC;&#x05E9;&#x05C1;&#x05E2; - pa&#x0302;sha&#x201B;</b> - <i>paw-shah'</i><p/>A primitive root (rather identical with <a href=\"#/H6585\">H6585</a> through the idea of <i>expansion</i>); to <i>break</i> away (from just authority), that is, <i>trespass</i>, <i>apostatize</i>, <i>quarrel: - </i>offend, rebel, revolt, transgress (-ion, -or)."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H6588\">H6588</a>, <a href=\"#/H6592\">H6592</a>, <a href=\"#/H6593\">H6593</a>, <a href=\"#/H6594\">H6594</a>, <a href=\"#/H6596\">H6596</a>, <a href=\"#/H6598\">H6598</a>, <a href=\"#/H6599\">H6599</a>"}]}